column5: So a pic of our new boat- picked it up on Thursday. A big ride and a big investment- hoping she turns out to be the boat I always dreamed of.
Good looking boat and I'll bet she'll handle big water with no problems.
love those boats, she's a beaut. Congrats!
You did well there. Nice and stable.Congrats !!!!
Come on. One photo and no motor shot.
Went Suzuki instead of Yamaha this time...225
Nice rig! One can dream... Haha one day
Went Suzuki instead of Yamaha this time...225  Nice. I am more of an A man then a T.
Wow, what a ridiculously awesome big water machine.  Congrats on you new rig
Yep, bought from George at Marshes, seems like a truly nice guy too.
